---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About — Kalyan AI"
	description="We build and host bespoke AI systems that remove friction from core business workflows."
>
	<main class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-5xl flex-col gap-12 px-6 pb-14">
		<header class="space-y-3 pt-4">
			<h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">About</h1>
			<p class="copy-narrow max-w-3xl text-lg text-[var(--muted)]">
				We build and host bespoke AI systems that remove friction from core business workflows.
			</p>
		</header>

		<section class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[360px_1fr] lg:items-start">
			<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-sm overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] shadow-sm aspect-[4/4.5]">
				<img
					class="h-full w-full object-cover"
					src="/images/1761512653.png"
					alt="Zax Kalyan"
					loading="lazy"
					decoding="async"
					style="object-position: 50% 12%;"
				/>
			</div>

			<div class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">Founder</h2>
				<p class="copy-narrow text-[var(--muted)]">
					I’m Zax Kalyan, founder of Kalyan AI. I’ve spent 15+ years leading and growing businesses under real-world pressure — owning P&L, building teams, and delivering results across industries.
				</p>
				<p class="copy-narrow text-[var(--muted)]">
					Kalyan AI is built around a simple idea: bespoke AI systems should fit the way your business actually runs. We design, build, and host systems that turn messy inputs into clear outputs — so decisions, follow-ups, and reporting happen reliably, with proper ownership and oversight.
				</p>
				<p class="copy-narrow text-[var(--muted)]">
					I’m also a contributor and shareholder at Nuvo Labs, a deep-tech AI research company. That proximity to research helps inform the technical choices we make, while keeping delivery focused on what matters day-to-day: reliability, control, and measurable impact.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="space-y-8">
			<div class="space-y-2">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">What we do</h2>
				<p class="max-w-3xl text-[var(--muted)]">
					We design, build, and operate hosted AI systems that respect how your business already works. Each system is tailored to your data, decisions, and owners—so your team gains clarity without more tools to manage.
				</p>
				<p class="max-w-3xl text-[var(--muted)]">
					You keep control and oversight; we handle the engineering, hosting, and steady improvements.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="space-y-3">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">How we work</h2>
				<ol class="space-y-2 text-[var(--muted)]">
					<li><span class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">Discover:</span> We map your current workflows, data, and decision points.</li>
					<li><span class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">Build:</span> We assemble the hosted AI layer with safeguards and clear ownership.</li>
					<li><span class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">Deploy:</span> We launch with you, monitor outcomes, and keep the system dependable.</li>
					<li><span class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">Improve:</span> We refine prompts, data flows, and reporting based on real usage.</li>
				</ol>
			</div>

			<!-- WHAT YOU GET START -->
			<section class="mt-10 space-y-3">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">What you get</h2>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-[var(--muted)]">
					<li><span class="font-medium text-[var(--text)]">Discovery and system design</span> — map workflows, inputs, decisions, and owners.</li>
					<li><span class="font-medium text-[var(--text)]">Build and integration</span> — connect to your data and operational tools.</li>
					<li><span class="font-medium text-[var(--text)]">Hosted operation</span> — monitoring, reliability, and steady improvements.</li>
					<li><span class="font-medium text-[var(--text)]">Training and handover</span> — your team knows how to use it day one.</li>
					<li><span class="font-medium text-[var(--text)]">Ongoing support</span> — fixes, refinements, and iteration based on real usage.</li>
				</ul>
			</section>
			<!-- WHAT YOU GET END -->

			<div class="space-y-3">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">What you can expect</h2>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-[var(--muted)]">
					<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
						<span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)]/60"></span>
						<span>Clarity on decisions, owners, and timing.</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
						<span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)]/60"></span>
						<span>Speed without sacrificing oversight or compliance.</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
						<span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)]/60"></span>
						<span>Reliability from a hosted system that stays maintained and supported.</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>

		<div>
			<a
				class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-[var(--secondary)]"
				href="https://calendly.com/zaxkalyan/30min"
			>
				Book a call
			</a>
		</div>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">FAQs</h2>
			<div class="divide-y divide-[var(--border-subtle)] rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border-subtle)] bg-white/80">
				{[
					{
						q: 'What types of businesses do you work with?',
						a: 'SMEs where operations rely on people making repeat decisions from calls, documents, and pipelines. We focus on teams that value clarity and control.',
					},
					{
						q: 'How quickly can we ship a first version?',
						a: 'Most first versions go live in 2–4 weeks once we have access to your processes and data examples. We keep the initial scope tight to show value early.',
					},
					{
						q: 'Do you host the system for us?',
						a: 'Yes. We host, monitor, and maintain the system so you do not need extra infrastructure or support staff to keep it reliable.',
					},
					{
						q: 'What about data security and access control?',
						a: 'We set clear data boundaries, least-privilege access, and audit trails. Ownership and permissions stay defined for your team.',
					},
					{
						q: 'Can this connect to our existing tools and workflows?',
						a: 'Yes. We integrate with your current systems and processes so the hosted AI layer fits how you already work.',
					},
					{
						q: 'How do pricing and ongoing support work?',
						a: 'We scope a build fee for the first version, then provide a hosting and support plan that covers monitoring, fixes, and iterative improvements.',
					},
					{
						q: 'What do you need from us to get started?',
						a: 'Access to the people, examples, and systems that show how you work today, plus a clear owner for decisions. We handle the rest.',
					},
				].map((item) => (
					<details class="group px-4 py-3 text-[var(--muted)]">
						<summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-3 text-[var(--brand-navy)] font-semibold transition hover:text-[var(--brand-navy-light)] focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-[var(--primary)] focus-visible:ring-offset-0">
							<span>{item.q}</span>
							<span class="text-sm text-[var(--muted)] group-open:rotate-45 transition">+</span>
						</summary>
						<div class="pt-2 text-[var(--muted)]">
							<p>{item.a}</p>
						</div>
					</details>
				))}
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
